title: Various Artists - Navigatorz Fresh!! Indie Playlist June 2011
description:
Year 2011. is here now, it's been some time since we've been doing these playlists, a big thank you to all of you who supported us and downloaded our lists up to now - this year we're gonna try and make them better and FRESHER!! every time...
We will, of course, continue with NAVIGATORZ indie playlist each month,...Hope you like them, your comments are, of course, welcome!

Anyone who is interested in sending your own stuff (via links to downloads), we would gladly listen to your music and include it in our list or radio show if we find it good, so more people would hear it...

As always, our own radio show is on the internet radio station http://radio.elektrana.net/ , every Tuesday 7pm CET. There you will be able to hear some new stuff before we upload it on the net.

This month exclusively as artwork one picture from Kurdistan. This month also more electronic, and indietronica singles we found. We hope you would like it.


Best regards
Navigatorz team

P.S. Also in July NAVIGATOR FRESH!! INDIE PLAYLIST LIVE on Elektrana Stage @ EXIT FESTIVAL 2011

P.s. of course, if you like the music, support the artists and buy their music!

NAVIGATOR, music team producing beats,grooves and much more...And an awesome DJ team and a soundsystem as well proudly presents:

NAVIGATORZ FRESH!! INDIE PLAYLIST JUNE 2011

NAVIGATORZ FRESH!! INDIE PLAYLIST contains the team's choice when it comes to independent music acts,ranging from guitar, electronic,acts to so called "indietronica" and experimental sounds...
Enjoy!
